{"tid":349828,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經]清水灣火雞大學ocamp指南","createTime":"2017-08-06T22:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T22:46:27.000Z","uid":55742,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d25b406fb881d0d79466370d3a11719eba319b26","tid":349828,"uid":55742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T22:42:26.000Z","msg":"想入科大柱磨柱既咁多位DSE考生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一年一度既reg day就快到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n果日係你人生唯一一次喺科大俾班女女圍住你既機會&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過千其唔好以為自己好撚型好撚charm先俾女圍，佢地都係想你地班毒撚落搭報ocamp咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面就介紹下科大啲ocamp同hall，等你地班毒撚reg day入到嚟都無咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n科大既ocamp分為SU Ocamp, School Ocamp, Department Ocamp, ICA Ocamp同埋 Hall O <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最撚霉果個一定係SU OCamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但今年科大冇咗SU, 所以今年冇SU Ocamp啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSchool Ocamp就即係BSU, ESU, SSU 同埋HSSU搞既Ocamp&nbsp;<br />\n佢地自稱自己做大O既&nbsp;<br />\n通常跟返你自己個School玩返相應既Ocamp啦&nbsp;<br />\n聽講普遍School搞既Ocamp會相對霉少少，Ocamp每日都可以訓餐飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好處就係收得多人，你當可以識得多啲人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過如果本身報Ocamp budget有限，個人意見可以skip左大O唔玩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己就讀Business既，上年上高登都見啲人話霉撚到仆街最後無join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家一樣過得好開心，上堂又有friend陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就係Department Ocamp，我就主力講Busi，其他School等巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀Business既有Account, ISOM, Econ, Marketing, MSA 同埋Finance&nbsp;<br />\n仲有個RMBISA就係Student Association既<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">千其唔好以為讀咩Major/想揀咩Major就玩咩Soc</span><br />\n<br />\n咁樣諗而去揀會後悔一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為果個Society喺Academic方面幫到你既野其實十分有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己想玩邊個就玩邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩department相對大O可能會識得少人啲，但係同你自己果group ocamp朋友會firm啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據我觀察呢，最多人玩同最好玩既Ocamp就係Econ同MSA&nbsp;<br />\nEcon就有Beach Day可以睇女女濕身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMSA就有真火Campfire玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咸魚青菜各有所愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩個Soc啲女女都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他Soc啲Ocamp就相對小型&nbsp;<br />\n玩唔玩就自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b497b277366bac71c5e8257b5001ed164704b284","tid":349828,"uid":55742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T22:46:27.000Z","msg":"跟住就係ICA既Ocamp，即係興趣Soc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年新起既有Food Soc，睇個勢好似幾勁咁，同埋個Camp內容好似都幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想玩Drama就join Drama Soc, 想跳舞就join Danso, 想做serive就玩四蛇（好似幾多女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）&nbsp;<br />\n鍾意動漫可以join動漫soc做毒拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n興趣Soc都係跟返自己興趣睇下玩唔玩，無咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊接住有Hall O，咁有莊既Hall就係Hall 1,2,3,4,5 好似仲有個Hall 6不過通常都無咩人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHall 1就最近Atrium, 聽講想跟某個Hall既路線，越玩就越癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHall 2就第二近Atrium，不過就好似無咩人同佢玩，好聽既就叫自成一角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHall3就要行少少大斜，聽人講都幾好玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHall4路程就同Hall3差唔多，以前就最癲既Hall成日take仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過近呢一兩年好似有少少回塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過算係錫女仔唔玩女既hall, 而男仔都係跳下蚊池咁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHall5就啲房最細，不過sell運動同音樂勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;好似已經攞左好多年Sports Champion, 同埋支莊啲人都幾warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}